  <mainDescription>The Context Designer should decide which CEs should be presented, when and how the presentation should occur. Issues
        related to human cognition should be considered, to avoid intrusiveness or information overload. The literature of
        information awareness provides many examples about how to present contextual information to improve cognition.&lt;br /></mainDescription>
  <purpose>The purpose of this activity is to design the presentation of the managed CE to the CSS Agents in order to enrich their
        knowledge about the Task being executed.&lt;br /></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
